import styled from '@emotion/styled'
import { Container, Paper, Stack } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
import { WalletPreview } from '../Components/Components'

const LoginWrap = styled(Paper)(({ theme }) => ({
    borderRadius: 15,
    width: '100%',
    maxWidth: 600,
    height: 300,
    overflow: 'hidden',
    display: 'flex',
    alignItems: 'center',
    padding: 10
}))
export default function Login() {
    return (
        <Container sx={{
            display: 'flex',
            justifyContent: 'center',
            alignItems
        }} fixed>
            <LoginWrap elevation={24}>
                <Stack>
                    <WalletPreview />
                </Stack>
            </LoginWrap>
        </Container>
    )
}
